{"tid":344224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍咗拖之後","createTime":"2017-08-02T06:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T09:00:23.000Z","uid":115353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"779ef4f6adb3e3059706a1e60c0382ec9faacb9b","tid":344224,"uid":115353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:34:36.000Z","msg":"有無人開始咗拍拖先知<br />\n原來自己一個係咁自由<br />\n做咩都唔會有人管<br />\n又唔使成日顧對方感受<br />\n自己鍾意點就點<br />\n又唔使成日諗住要點樣覆佢訊息<br />\n宜家拍拖之後每日都好似好忙咁<br />\n有時會諗自己啱唔啱拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無得拍嗰陣就好恨拍<br />\n有得拍嗰陣又有啲嚮往單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人有共鳴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪得我一個會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e48bd6215db6974c609f7fdfd3384c7d301844","tid":344224,"uid":115353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8927dfbbb0f53fec6dee8679ffbb91e0fbfcdcfd","tid":344224,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"對方好似咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申無拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fc3b1be3173080f40153ec74594bfcb23c067f","tid":344224,"uid":96979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"但又會唔捨得<br />\n一冇 就真係咩都冇<br />\n關心既資格都冇埋"},{"pid":"1999d2817d76384a39673155cc9ccb7af7f240d3","tid":344224,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"a0 留名"},{"pid":"9bc13eaa89f71ad035d792e7a9ff29cece31a34b","tid":344224,"uid":50819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"冇拍過拖已經知道係咁<br />\n所以冇拍<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95922b0daa6183bd10d4a620ba1899a8eadfd07d","tid":344224,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}